00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:02,440
基於真實故事

5
00:00:32,620 --> 00:00:37,380
1953年肯尼亞在基庫尤人組成的茅茅黨帶領下

6
00:00:37,410 --> 00:00:42,010
爆發了反對英國殖民統治的武裝起義

7
00:00:42,030 --> 00:00:46,730
在這場鬥爭中  數千人喪生

8
00:00:46,750 --> 00:00:51,740
超過一百萬基庫尤人被送入拘留營

9
00:00:51,770 --> 00:00:55,750
鬥爭終於贏來了獨立

10
00:00:55,780 --> 00:01:00,010
但是對很多人來說  過去難以釋懷

11
00:02:58,710 --> 00:03:01,710
片名:  「一年級生」

12
00:03:04,860 --> 00:03:07,450
同胞們，同胞們
My People, my people.

13
00:03:07,610 --> 00:03:10,160
現在，新政府宣佈
Now, the new government has announced

14
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:12,540
全民享受免費教育
free education for all.

15
00:03:12,700 --> 00:03:17,080
他們只要你出現帶著出生證明來
All they want is for you to turn up with a birth certificate.

16
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:21,670
一個會信守諾言的政府?  難以置信!
A government that keeps its promise? Unbelievable!

17
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:32,910
我兒子需要接受教育
My son needs to be educated.

18
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:35,750
他叫卡莫.切赫，卡莫.切赫 切赫！
Kamau Chege, Kamau Chege. Chege!

19
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:50,510
珍妮老師  珍妮老師!  過來  他要見你
Teacher Jane, Teacher Jane! Come on, he's asking for you.

20
00:04:50,670 --> 00:04:52,800
請過來一下! Please!

21
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:54,560
凱瑟琳老師!
Teacher Katherine!

22
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:57,260
凱瑟琳老師  你能來一下嗎?
Teacher Katherine, can you come?

23
00:04:57,430 --> 00:04:59,930
好的  請給我一點時間
OK, give me a moment, please.

24
00:05:00,100 --> 00:05:03,400
這張不是出生證  老媽媽  你不是最先到的
This is not a birth certificate. Mama, you are not the first.

25
00:05:09,810 --> 00:05:11,650
有什麼可以幫到你的? 老人家
May' help you, mzee?

26
00:05:11,810 --> 00:05:13,650
這裡是一所小學
This is a primary school.

27
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:22,440
"新政府承諾全民可免費接受初等教育"
"The new government promises free primary education for all"

28
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:25,970
老人家，他們指的是孩子，不是成年人
Mzee, they meant children, not adults.

29
00:05:25,990 --> 00:05:30,460
不  我親耳從收音機裡聽到的
No. I heard on the radio, with my own ears.

30
00:05:30,660 --> 00:05:33,090
他們說每個人都可以
They said everybody.

31
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:37,300
我們有200個學生卻只有50張桌子  看看這個
We have 200 students and only 50 desks. Look at this.

32
00:05:37,460 --> 00:05:40,340
我們不能把它們浪費在一個一隻腳進墳墓的老人身上
We can't waste them on an old man with one foot in the grave.

33
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:43,010
老人家，你的練習本在哪裡？
Mzee, where are your exercise books?

34
00:05:43,010 --> 00:05:46,400
你要有兩個練習本  以及一支鋒利的HB鉛筆
You need two, and one HB pencil, sharp,

35
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,930
一頭帶橡皮擦
with a rubber on one end.

36
00:05:48,100 --> 00:05:50,150
這些是入學規定
Those are the regulations.

37
00:05:56,300 --> 00:06:00,100
不，老人家，不
Pole, mzee. Pole.

38
00:06:17,860 --> 00:06:19,490
馬魯格  馬魯格
Maruge maruge

39
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:24,490
一起來喝酒吧!  人生苦短  啤酒甘美
Let's have a drink! Life is short beer is sweet

40
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:30,490
馬魯格才不屑跟我們一起喝酒呢!
Maruge doesn't care to drink with us!

41
00:06:32,150 --> 00:06:34,660
早上好  孩子們
Good morning, boys and girls.

42
00:06:34,810 --> 00:06:37,160
早上好，女士！
Good morning, madam!

43
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:41,080
你們好嗎? 很好，謝謝你，女士！
How are you? Fine, thank you, madam!

44
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:44,790
你們好嗎?  你好嗎? 夫人
How do you do? How do you do, madam?

45
00:06:44,950 --> 00:06:47,000
我很好，謝謝你們
I do very well, thank you.

46
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:50,710
我很高興你們都來到我的教室上課
I am so excited to have you here all in my classroom.

47
00:06:50,870 --> 00:06:53,670
歡迎 卡里布尼  請坐下
Welcome. Karibuni. Sit down, please.

48
00:06:53,840 --> 00:06:55,680
謝謝你，女士
Thank you, madam.

49
00:06:55,830 --> 00:06:58,840
現在，我知道你們有些人可能有點緊張
Now, I know that some of you may be a little nervous,

50
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,750
但是沒什麼好害怕的
but there's nothing to be afraid of.

51
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:04,680
學習就是要有樂趣，所以我們都是來這裡找樂趣的 
Learning is about having fun, so we are all here to have fun.

52
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:06,260
不是嗎? 是的
Si ndiyo? Yes.

53
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:08,560
好的，讓我查一下 每個人都有自己的書嗎？
Alright, let me check. Has everybody got their books?

54
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,890
是的! 非常好!
Yes! Very good!

55
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:13,430
而且每個人都有鉛筆嗎？有!
And has everybody got their pencils? Yes!

56
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:17,230
好啊! 好的...我聽到有人說沒有  誰說沒有的?
OK. Good...I heard a few noes. Who said no?

57
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:20,200
好吧，噢! 佛蘭西斯，你能來發一下鉛筆嗎? 拜託
OK, well, Francis, can you give out some pencils, please?

58
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:22,610
好了...OK...

59
00:07:22,780 --> 00:07:25,620
帕里斯和波林  請到前面來
Paris and Pauline, come to the front, please.

60
00:07:25,780 --> 00:07:27,950
所以 大家記得明天要帶你的課本和你的鉛筆來
So, everyone, tomorrow, your books and your pencils.

61
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:30,870
是的 好的 非常好  非常好
Yes. OK, very good, very good.

62
00:07:32,870 --> 00:抱歉07:34,840
抱歉，抱歉，對不起
Sorry, sorry, excuse me.

63
00:07:46,590 --> 00:07:50,140
回家去吧!  老人家  我看得出來你生活很艱難
Go home, mzee. I can see you've had a hard life.

64
00:07:50,300 --> 00:07:52,270
回家好好休息吧!
Go home and rest in peace.

65
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:53,980
好好休息?
Rest in peace?

66
00:07:54,140 --> 00:07:55,640
我還沒死 I'm not dead.

67
00:07:55,810 --> 00:07:57,400
聽著 老人家...
Look, mzee...

68
00:07:57,560 --> 00:08:02,910
我叫奇曼尼·囊·馬魯格
My name is Kimani Ng'ang'a Maruge.

69
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:07,040
噢! 奇曼尼·囊·馬魯格
Well, Kimani Ng'ang'a Maruge,

70
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:10,120
我們不能接收沒穿校服的人
we cannot accept anyone without a school uniform,

71
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:13,330
而且這也意味著要穿校鞋
and that means school shoes too.

72
00:08:13,490 --> 00:08:16,210
而且你沒錢買這些東西
And you do not have money for such things.

73
00:08:16,370 --> 00:08:17,540
珍妮? Jane?

74
00:08:23,590 --> 00:08:28,310
老人家，為什麼你那麼老了還想上學
Mzee, why does someone as old as you want to go to school?

75
00:08:28,470 --> 00:08:30,390
我想學習閱讀
I want to learn to read.

76
00:08:30,550 --> 00:08:33,350
我們的學生已經太多了
We've got too many pupils already.

77
00:08:34,680 --> 00:08:37,060
我希望我能幫助你
I wish I could help you.

78
00:08:37,230 --> 00:08:40,950
我很抱歉 不
I'm sorry. Pole.

79
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:25,970
"總統辦公室"
"Office of the president"

80
00:10:18,870 --> 00:10:20,960
好的 我們到了
Alright, here we are.

81
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:25,050
好吧，非常感謝  謝謝
OK, asante sana. Asante.

82
00:10:25,210 --> 00:10:26,760
再見  老師
Goodbye, Teacher.

83
00:10:31,130 --> 00:10:33,050
你記得我跟你說過的那個老頭嗎？
You know that old man I told you about?

84
00:10:33,220 --> 00:10:36,440
他又回來了
He came back again.

85
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:39,020
我希望你沒有讓他入學
I hope you did not let him in.

86
00:10:39,180 --> 00:10:41,780
這個可憐的老男孩可能老了
The poor old boy might be senile.

87
00:10:41,930 --> 00:10:44,480
你為什麼不堅持你能贏的戰役，嗯？
Why don't you stick to battles you can win, hm?

88
00:10:44,650 --> 00:10:46,740
比如找更多的桌子
Like finding more desks.

89
00:10:49,190 --> 00:10:50,660
你這周過得怎樣?
How was your week?

90
00:10:50,820 --> 00:10:54,450
瑞典公司沒付我咨詢費
The Swedish company hasn't paid me the consulting fee.

91
00:10:54,610 --> 00:10:57,490
政府的工作開始聽起來很有吸引力
The government job is starting to sound very appealing.

92
00:10:57,660 --> 00:11:00,040
除了必須待在奈洛比做全職這一點
Except it had to be full time in Nairobi,

93
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:02,380
然後我們就再也見不到對方了
and then we'd never see each other at all.

94
00:11:02,540 --> 00:11:04,510
如果你也來奈洛比的話就不會了
Not if you came to Nairobi.

95
00:11:04,670 --> 00:11:09,550
我們將住在一所大房子裡，生孩子
We'll live in a big house, make babies.

96
00:11:09,710 --> 00:11:11,590
生一群小歐賓舒
Have a little bunch of Obinchus.

97
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:15,600
查爾斯，我不能
Charles, I can't.

98
00:11:15,760 --> 00:11:17,760
學校需要我
The school needs me.

99
00:11:17,930 --> 00:11:19,770
那我呢?
What about me?

100
00:11:21,770 --> 00:11:23,360
你把我難倒了
You've got me.

101
00:12:03,940 --> 00:12:04,790
你好女士  我要買些衣服
Hello, ma'am I need to buy some clothes

102
00:12:06,930 --> 00:12:08,620
你穿這件好看
It looks good on you

103
00:12:08,880 --> 00:12:10,630
這件多少錢
How much is this one

104
00:12:10,880 --> 00:12:12,030
我算你便宜點
I'll make it cheaper for you

105
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:15,630
幫我放到一邊
Put this aside for me 

106
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:33,730
你日子過得真滋潤呀!
You are living a good life!

107
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:36,630
帶著三個老婆買東西
Shopping with three wives

108
00:13:39,530 --> 00:13:42,530
我們這裡五個孩子共用一張桌子 先生
We've got five children to a desk here, sir.

109
00:13:42,700 --> 00:13:45,200
還有孩子坐地板上
There are children sitting on the floor.

110
00:13:45,370 --> 00:13:48,170
他們不能這樣學習，奇普托先生
They can't work like this, Mr Kipruto.

111
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:56,100
你需要為每一個新生的孩子準備一份表格，一式三份？
You need a form for every single new child, in triplicate?

112
00:13:56,250 --> 00:13:59,050
不，你不是認真的 我沒時間這麼做，奇普托先生
No, you can't be serious. I don't have time to do that, Mr Kipruto.

113
00:13:59,210 --> 00:14:01,640
你能不能僅僅相信我的話?
Could you not just take my word for it?

114
00:14:01,800 --> 00:14:05,100
是的，我知道，要按規定
Yes, I know, regulations.

115
00:14:05,260 --> 00:14:07,390
我也祝你日安，奇普托先生
Good day to you too, Mr Kipruto.

116
00:14:08,850 --> 00:14:10,570
我該怎麼辦? 阿爾佛雷德
What am I to do, Alfred?

117
00:14:10,730 --> 00:14:15,570
我們尊敬的首長已做出了一項行政決定
Our esteemed superintendent has made one of his executive decisions.

118
00:14:16,980 --> 00:14:18,360
你一定要來看看這個
You've got to see this.

119
00:14:18,530 --> 00:14:20,490
什麼? What?

120
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:39,260
你不會輕易放棄的，對吧? 馬魯格
You don't give up easily, do you, Maruge?

121
00:14:39,420 --> 00:14:41,720
你不能上當
You can't fall for this.

122
00:14:41,880 --> 00:14:44,180
當局會找你麻煩的
You'll be asking for trouble with the authorities.

123
00:14:44,340 --> 00:14:46,140
你知道他是對的，馬魯格？
You know he's right, Maruge?

124
00:14:46,300 --> 00:14:48,730
我怎麼向教育委員會交代?
What will I say to the board of education?

125
00:14:48,890 --> 00:14:50,640
嗯? Hm?

126
00:14:50,810 --> 00:14:53,980
我該怎麼跟孩子們的父母交代?
What will I say to the parents?

127
00:14:54,140 --> 00:14:56,360
我會當個好學生
I'll be a good pupil.

128
00:14:57,690 --> 00:14:59,160
我會努力學習
I'll work very hard.

129
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:00,690
如果奇浦路托發現...
If Kipruto finds out...

130
00:15:00,860 --> 00:15:03,110
奇浦路托不是這裡的頭兒，阿爾弗雷德
Kipruto's not the head here, Alfred.

131
00:15:03,280 --> 00:15:05,580
而是我 I am.

132
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:14,250
讓他入學 Let him in.

133
00:15:14,410 --> 00:15:18,040
我正在做一個行政決策
I'm making an executive decision.

134
00:15:19,460 --> 00:15:21,300
批准馬魯格入學
Let Maruge in.

135
00:15:33,520 --> 00:15:36,860
馬魯格? 歡迎
Maruge? Welcome.

136
00:15:37,020 --> 00:15:38,610
歡迎 Karibu.

137
00:16:11,010 --> 00:16:12,640
謝謝 Thank you.

138
00:16:12,810 --> 00:16:14,850
佛蘭西斯，回座位坐好
Francis, take your seat.

139
00:16:18,730 --> 00:16:21,980
同學們，今天我們來了個新同學
Class, we have a new student today,

140
00:16:22,150 --> 00:16:24,570
而他德名字叫馬魯格
and his name is Maruge.

141
00:16:24,730 --> 00:16:27,450
歡迎，馬魯格!
Welcome, Maruge!

142
00:16:27,830 --> 00:16:31,250
我來這裡跟你們一起學習

143
00:16:34,410 --> 00:16:36,040
珍妮弗，請舉一下妳的手
Jennifer, raise your hand, please.

144
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:38,670
想讓你坐在珍妮弗旁邊
I would like you to go and sit next to Jennifer

145
00:16:38,830 --> 00:16:40,430
就在後面那裡，請，馬魯格
at the back there, please, Maruge.

146
00:16:40,580 --> 00:16:43,800
如果我坐得太遠，我就看不見了 我不能
If I sit far, I can't see. I can't.

147
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:45,340
好吧! OK.

148
00:16:45,510 --> 00:16:48,850
嗯...蘇珊，你能坐在那裡嗎？
Uh...Suzanne, can you sit there?

149
00:16:49,010 --> 00:16:52,260
莎拉，你能坐尼維旁邊嗎？拜託
Sarah, can you sit next to Niva, please?

150
00:16:52,430 --> 00:16:54,560
馬魯格，你可以坐在那裡
Maruge, you can sit there.

151
00:16:54,720 --> 00:16:57,690
坐在尼維旁邊，好嗎？莎拉
Sit next to Niva, OK, Sarah?

152
00:16:57,850 --> 00:17:00,270
往後坐一點  好嗎? 很好
Back down. Yes? Good.

153
00:17:02,730 --> 00:17:04,570
我們開始上課!
Let's begin!

154
00:17:04,730 --> 00:17:07,410
打開練習本
Open your exercise books.

155
00:17:07,570 --> 00:17:09,910
鉛筆好又尖
Pencils nice and sharp.

156
00:17:10,070 --> 00:17:11,990
好又尖!
Nice and sharp!

157
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:14,080
我的鉛筆是我的朋友
My pencil is my friend.

158
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:16,710
我把它一直握在手
I keep him to the end.

159
00:17:16,870 --> 00:17:19,460
我的鉛筆是我的朋友
My pencil is my friend.

160
00:17:19,620 --> 00:17:22,250
我把它一直握在手
I keep him to the end.

161
00:17:22,420 --> 00:17:28,050
好的 今天我們從小寫字母開始學
OK, we are going to begin with small letters today,

162
00:17:28,210 --> 00:17:31,940
以字母“a”開始，好嗎？
beginning with the letter 'A', OK?

163
00:17:32,090 --> 00:17:36,350
這就是我們寫小寫字母“a”的方式
And this is how we write our small letter 'A'.

164
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:42,360
好吧，先是胖胖的，然後瘦瘦的
OK, a fatty, a thinny.

165
00:17:42,520 --> 00:17:47,490
胖胖的，瘦瘦的
A fatty, a thinny.

166
00:17:47,650 --> 00:17:51,280
請繼續寫你的小寫字母"a"
Please continue writing your lower-case 'A's.

167
00:17:51,450 --> 00:17:54,200
布蘭登，布蘭登 對不起，親愛的
Brendan, Brendan. Sorry, darling.

168
00:17:54,370 --> 00:17:57,540
馬魯格，鉛筆是這樣握的
Maruge, this is how you hold a pencil.

169
00:17:58,540 --> 00:18:03,210
好的，你把它夾在你的拇指和食指之間
OK, you hold it between your thumb and your first finger.

170
00:18:03,380 --> 00:18:06,720
非常好  然後你輕輕地按，不要太用力，好嗎？
Very good. And you press lightly not too hard, OK?

171
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:08,430
非常好 Very good.

