Kikuyus work like stallions. They're very...

358
00:38:59,380 --> 00:39:02,010
馬魯格，住手! 馬魯格!
Maruge, stop it! Maruge!

359
00:39:03,490 --> 00:39:04,920
住手! 嘿!
Stop it! Hey!

360
00:39:05,220 --> 00:39:08,720
嘿，嘿，嘿！這是怎麼回事？
Hey, hey, hey! What's going on here?

361
