telling me about an old man in one of my primary schools!

363
00:39:15,810 --> 00:39:18,030
他是誰? 為什麼他穿著校服?
Who is he? Why is he in school uniform?

364
00:39:20,070 --> 00:39:21,940
他叫馬魯格
His name is Maruge.

365
00:39:22,120 --> 00:39:23,750
老人家 M Mzee

366
00:39:24,660 --> 00:39:26,490
誰准許你進來的
Who allowed you in

367
00:39:32,000 --> 00:39:34,370
他想上學，所以我就讓他進來了
He wanted to come to school, so I let him.

368
00:39:34,540 --> 00:39:36,590
你什麼意思? 這是一所小學
What do you mean? This is a primary school.

369
00:39:36,750 --> 00:39:39,340
先生，政府說每個人都有上學的權利
Sir, the government said everybody has the right to go to school.

370
00:39:39,530 --> 00:39:43,750
僅僅因為我們的政客愚蠢並不意味著我們也必須愚蠢！
Just because our politicians are stupid doesn't mean we have to be as well!

371
00:39:43,880 --> 00:39:45,480
他不能待在這裡
He can't stay here.

372
00:39:45,630 --> 00:39:48,390
成年人必須去成人學校
Adults must go to the adult school.

373
00:39:48,560 --> 00:39:50,610
現在，確保他現在離開這裡
Now, see to it that he leaves here now.

374
00:39:52,930 --> 00:39:56,480
先生，他與英國人作戰
Sir, he fought the British.

375
00:39:56,650 --> 00:40:00,240
他被囚禁在拘留營裡 哦，原來是茅茅黨的，蛤？
He was imprisoned in the camps. Oh, Mau Mau, huh?

376
00:40:00,400 --> 00:40:02,740
典型基庫尤人  我早該知道的
Typical Kikuyu. I should have known.

377
00:40:02,900 --> 00:40:04,870
你說什麼? Excuse me?

378
00:40:05,030 --> 00:40:06,750
我以為部落主義已經結束了
I thought tribalism was over.

379
00:40:06,910 --> 00:40:08,950
這跟部落主義沒關係
This has nothing to do with tribalism.

380
00:40:09,130 --> 00:40:10,970
這是為了做對學校有利的事
It's about doing what's right for the school.

381
00:40:11,000 --> 00:40:14,470
像他這樣的老人不應該待在滿是孩子的教室裡 
An old man like him does not belong in a classroom full of children.

382
00:40:14,730 --> 00:40:17,650
現在，這件事我們到辦公室再繼續說
Now, we'll continue this conversation in the office.

383
00:40:29,890 --> 00:40:31,260
馬魯格...Maruge...

384
00:40:31,430 --> 00:40:32,850
他們是血腥的卡倫金人
He's a bloody Kalenjin.

385
00:40:33,010 --> 00:40:34,690
你不也是嗎? 馬魯格
You too, Maruge?

386
00:40:34,850 --> 00:40:38,150
你知道You were either for them or you were against them,
獨立後，我們都成了肯尼亞人
You know, after independence, we all became Kenyans.

387
00:40:38,310 --> 00:40:39,690
卡倫金人是忠誠的！
The Kalenjins were loyalists!

388
00:40:39,860 --> 00:40:42,110
我的家人也效忠英國人!
So were my family loyal to the British!

389
00:40:42,270 --> 00:40:44,650
想要活命的每個人都是!
So was everybody if they wanted to stay alive!

390
00:40:44,850 --> 00:40:48,980
別那樣看著我  英國人從來沒有給人們一個選擇
And don't look at me like that. The British never gave people a choice.

391
00:40:49,110 --> 00:40:51,160
你要嘛支持他們，或者你要嘛反對他們
You were either for them or you were against them,

392
00:40:51,320 --> 00:40:53,250
而如果你反對他們，他們就殺你
and if you were against them, they killed you.

393
00:40:53,450 --> 00:40:56,700
我有過孩子
I had children.

394
00:40:56,830 --> 00:40:58,960
兩個孩子!
Two children!

395
00:41:00,040 --> 00:41:01,960
我有過一個家!
I had a family!

396
00:41:03,590 --> 00:41:05,560
英國人把他們都殺了
The British killed them.

397
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:08,810
我們作出了選擇
We chose.

398
00:41:08,970 --> 00:41:11,850
基庫尤人作出了選擇
The Kikuyus chose.

399
00:41:12,010 --> 00:41:13,980
而我們也付出了代價
And we paid.

400
00:41:15,060 --> 00:41:16,520
我們付出了代價!
We paid!

401
00:41:33,160 --> 00:41:36,160
回去上課，回去上課，回去上課，回去上課
Come to class. Come to class, come to class, come to class.

402
00:41:37,540 --> 00:41:39,670
回去上課，回去上課
Go to class, go to class.

403
00:42:03,480 --> 00:42:05,860
他說我必須讓馬魯格退學
He says I've got to get rid of Maruge.

404
00:42:06,900 --> 00:42:08,990
他要送他到成人學校
He's sending him off to the adult school.

405
00:42:09,150 --> 00:42:10,870
他的同情心哪去了?
Where is his compassion?

406
00:42:11,030 --> 00:42:12,870
珍妮，珍妮，別說了
Jane, Jane, just stop.

407
00:42:13,030 --> 00:42:14,660
他不是那麼說的
That's not what he's saying.

408
00:42:14,830 --> 00:42:17,250
他只是說馬魯格不能上小學
He's just saying Maruge cannot go to children's school.

409
00:42:17,410 --> 00:42:18,830
你為什麼要幫他辯護?
Why are you defending him?

410
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:22,300
英國人殺了他的家人  我們有責任去幫他
The British killed his family. We have a duty to help him.

411
00:42:22,470 --> 00:42:25,390
茅茅黨也殺人，好嗎？
The Mau Mau killed people too, OK?

412
00:42:25,540 --> 00:42:28,550
但是這跟老人上小學的事情無關
But that's got nothing to do with an old man going to a children's school.

413
00:42:28,710 --> 00:42:29,710
好的 Fine.

414
00:42:29,890 --> 00:42:32,490
沒有人會為馬魯格而戰，所以我會的
No-one's going to fight for Maruge, so I will.

415
00:42:32,630 --> 00:42:34,760
好的，請不要越過奇普托的頭
OK, please do not go over Kipruto's head.

416
00:42:34,930 --> 00:42:37,180
我跟這些人一起工作而且我知道他們的情況
I work with these people and I know how they are.

417
00:42:37,350 --> 00:42:39,650
他們對此並不友好
They don't take kindly to this.

418
00:42:39,810 --> 00:42:41,480
你知道我總是站在你這邊的
You know I'm always on your side.

419
00:42:41,670 --> 00:42:43,850
愛你 再見
Love you. 'Bye.

420
00:42:50,240 --> 00:42:53,710
我很感激你的關心，但我無能為力
I appreciate your concern, but my hands are tied.

421
00:42:53,860 --> 00:42:56,370
馬魯格很努力學習
Maruge is such a hard worker.

422
00:42:57,410 --> 00:42:59,830
他是孩子們的好榜樣
He's a great role model for the children.

423
00:43:00,000 --> 00:43:03,420
如果我們讓馬魯格入學，那我們怎麼拒絕其他人?
If we let Maruge in, how can we refuse others?

424
00:43:03,580 --> 00:43:05,760
我們的學校可能會擠滿了老人
Our schools could be flooded with old people.

425
00:43:05,920 --> 00:43:07,420
這將剝奪
This would be taking away

426
00:43:07,590 --> 00:43:10,260
我們為孩子們所需的寶貴資源
from the precious resources we need for our children.

427
00:43:12,800 --> 00:43:14,770
感謝您抽出時間，秘書長女士
Thank you for your time, Madam Secretary.

428
00:43:14,930 --> 00:43:17,350
不客氣 You're welcome.

429
00:43:17,510 --> 00:43:21,640
歐賓舒夫人，有個跟丹麥政府合作的顧問
Mrs Obinchu, one of the consultants working with the Danish Government,

430
00:43:21,810 --> 00:43:23,190
叫查爾斯·歐賓舒
Charles Obinchu.

431
00:43:23,350 --> 00:43:25,020
查爾斯是我丈夫
Charles is my husband.

432
00:43:25,190 --> 00:43:27,940
代我想他問好 我會的
Give him my best. I will.

433
00:43:28,110 --> 00:43:33,580
歐賓舒夫人，孩子是肯尼亞的未來
Mrs Obinchu, the children are Kenya's future.

434
00:43:57,640 --> 00:43:59,430
對不起，馬魯格
I'm sorry, Maruge.

435
00:44:34,840 --> 00:44:36,590
我沒錢，沒錢
I have no money, no money.

436
00:44:36,760 --> 00:44:38,140
天下沒有免費的午餐
There's nothing for free.

437
00:44:38,300 --> 00:44:39,890
你太老了，走不動的
You cannot go, you're too old.

438
00:45:02,960 --> 00:45:06,550
"成人學習中心  力求優秀"
"Adult learning centers strive for excellence"

439
00:45:41,740 --> 00:45:44,410
所以今天我們重點討論單數和複數
So today we're focusing on singular and plural.

440
00:45:44,580 --> 00:45:46,540
讓我們從"床"開始，好嗎？
Let's start with 'bed', alright?

441
00:45:46,700 --> 00:45:48,960
所以，"bed"，bed的複數形式是beds
So, 'bed', the plural for 'bed' is 'beds'.

442
00:45:49,120 --> 00:45:51,800
那就是B-E-D-S
That's B-E-D-S.

443
00:45:51,960 --> 00:45:53,880
好的，所以你只要加一個"S"
Alright, so you just add an 'S'.

444
