00:46:17,860 --> 00:46:19,360
再見! 謝謝!
Kwa heri! Asante!

450
00:46:19,530 --> 00:46:20,900
待會見，老師
See you later, Teacher.

451
00:46:21,070 --> 00:46:22,740
馬魯格  你在這裡幹什麼?
Maruge, what are you doing here?

452
00:46:22,910 --> 00:46:24,870
進來吧! Come inside.

453
00:46:25,030 --> 00:46:28,750
我發誓要從英國人手裡奪回土地
I took the oath to get our land back from the British.

454
00:46:28,910 --> 00:46:32,880
馬魯格，你不必告訴我這些
Maruge, you don't have to tell me this.

455
00:46:33,040 --> 00:46:35,790
基庫尤人沒有土地意味著什麼?
What is Kikuyu without land?

456
00:46:35,960 --> 00:46:39,180
馬賽人最看重的是牛
The Masai, it's cattle.

457
00:46:39,340 --> 00:46:41,640
但我們最看重的是土地
But for us, it's land.

458
00:46:41,800 --> 00:46:45,180
這就是我們抗爭的原因
That's why we were fighting.

459
00:46:46,680 --> 00:46:50,230
但如果我們不識字，我們什麼都不是
But we are nothing if we cannot read.

460
00:46:50,390 --> 00:46:52,770
我們毫無用處
We are useless.

461
00:46:58,860 --> 00:47:00,950
當我小時候
When I was a boy,

462
00:47:01,110 --> 00:47:03,410
沒有錢用於教育
there was no money for education.

463
00:47:04,910 --> 00:47:07,630
我在一個白人的農場工作
I worked on a white man's farm.

464
00:47:09,620 --> 00:47:13,040
然後就為自由而戰
Then came the fight for freedom.

465
00:47:14,120 --> 00:47:15,170
馬魯格...Maruge...

466
00:47:15,330 --> 00:47:16,800
我有一封信
I have a letter.

467
00:47:16,960 --> 00:47:18,340
你這話是什麼意思?
What do you mean?

468
00:47:18,500 --> 00:47:21,550
這就是我來學校的原因
That's why I came to the school.

469
00:47:21,710 --> 00:47:25,090
我必須親自看
I must read it for myself.

470
00:47:26,850 --> 00:47:29,850
我必須去理解
I have to understand.

471
00:47:30,890 --> 00:47:32,560
求你了 Please.

472
00:47:33,640 --> 00:47:37,020
教我認字，歐賓舒夫人
Teach me to read, Mrs Obinchu.

473
00:47:42,320 --> 00:47:46,450
噢! 我知道我們以前談過很多次關於馬魯格的事
Well, I know we've had this conversation many times before about Maruge,

474
00:47:46,610 --> 00:47:49,790
但我想知道你是否願意重新考慮一下
but I was wondering if you might be willing to reconsider.

475
00:47:49,950 --> 00:47:52,500
奇普托先生，他們只是在成人學校混日子
Mr Kipruto, they just mess around at the adult school.

476
