他什麼也沒學到
He didn't learn a thing.

477
00:47:56,540 --> 00:47:58,010
是的 Yes.

478
00:47:58,170 --> 00:48:00,260
是的，我當然很感激
Yes, of course I'm grateful.

479
00:48:01,710 --> 00:48:03,260
再見 Kwa heri.

480
00:48:06,130 --> 00:48:08,260
馬魯格，對不起  我已經盡力了...
Maruge, I'm very sorry. I've done everything...

481
00:48:08,430 --> 00:48:10,480
那個該死的奇普托可以下地獄！
That bloody Kipruto can go to hell!

482
00:48:10,640 --> 00:48:12,110
成人學校總比沒有強...
The adult school is better than nothing...

