00:49:18,870 --> 00:49:20,750
我是來說再見的
I came to say goodbye.

505
00:49:23,000 --> 00:49:26,880
我告訴他們山羊不識字
I told them a goat cannot read.

506
00:49:28,970 --> 00:49:31,770
山羊不會寫自己的名字
A goat cannot write his name.

507
00:49:32,890 --> 00:49:37,770
他們必須努力學習，否則他們會像我一樣
They must study hard, or they'll be like me

508
00:49:37,940 --> 00:49:42,250
一個不比那隻山羊好多少的老人
an old man no better than that goat.

509
00:49:49,240 --> 00:49:53,040
你知道，山羊是非常聰明的動物
You know, goats are very clever animals.

510
00:49:53,200 --> 00:49:55,290
他們從不放棄
They never give up.

511
00:49:57,160 --> 00:50:00,040
我們可以好好向他們學習
We can learn a very good lesson from them.

512
00:50:05,170 --> 00:50:09,170
同學們，我有重要的事情宣佈
Class, I have an important announcement.

513
00:50:09,350 --> 00:50:14,350
從現在起，馬魯格將成為我的助教
From now on, Maruge is going to be my teaching assistant.

514
00:50:14,510 --> 00:50:17,520
幹得好，幹得好，馬魯格
Well done, well done, Maruge.

515
00:50:17,680 --> 00:50:19,100
我印象深刻
I'm impressed.

516
00:50:19,280 --> 00:50:21,500
你是怎麼讓他們表現得這麼好的？
How did you get them all to behave so well?

517
00:50:21,640 --> 00:50:27,200
我告訴他們，如果他們不規矩，我就用棍子打他們
I told them if they didn't behave, I'll clobber them with my stick.

518
00:50:29,610 --> 00:50:31,160
馬魯格! Maruge!

519
00:51:19,080 --> 00:51:20,800
等等，馬魯格先生來了！
Wait a minute, there's Mr Maruge!

520
00:51:20,950 --> 00:51:22,330
馬魯格先生來了
There's Mr Maruge.

521
00:51:22,500 --> 00:51:24,090
馬魯格先生，馬魯格先生
Mr Maruge, Mr Maruge.

522
00:51:29,840 --> 00:51:31,510
好了，好了! Alright, alright!

523
