拜託，拜託，如果我們接受採訪，至少要有秩序地進行
Please, please, if we're going to do this, let us at least do it in an orderly way.

524
00:51:35,760 --> 00:51:39,230
如果你想和馬魯格說話，一次問一個問題
If you want to speak to Maruge, one question at a time.

